<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Patient Info</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,600,700">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/app.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="navbar">
        <div class="chettinad">
            <img src="/photos/ChettinadLogo2.png" alt="img"><h1>Chettinad Hospital</h1>
        </div>
        <a class= "btn btn-warning" href="/logout">Sign Out</a>
    </header>
    
    <br><br>
    <br>
    <div class="col-6 offset-3">
        <form action="/doctor/<%= doctor._id %>?_method=PUT" method="POST" novalidate class="validation-form editDoctorForm">
            <h1 class="text-center">Edit Profile</h1>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label" for="username">Name:</label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="username" name="doctor[username]" value="<%= doctor.username %>" required>
                <div class="valid-feedback">
                    Looks Good!
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label" for="patientID">Doctor ID:</label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="patientID" name="doctor[ID]" value="<%= doctor.ID %>" required>
                <div class="valid-feedback">
                    Looks Good!
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label" for="mbnum">Mobile Number:</label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="mbnum" name="doctor[mobile]" value="<%= doctor.mobile %>" required>
                <div class="valid-feedback">
                    Looks Good!
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label" for="age">Age:</label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="age" name="doctor[age]" value="<%= doctor.age %>" required>
                <div class="valid-feedback">
                    Looks Good!
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label" for="sex">Sex:</label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="sex" name="doctor[sex]" value="<%= doctor.sex %>" required>
                <div class="valid-feedback">
                    Looks Good!
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label" for="speciality">Speciality:</label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="speciality" name="doctor[speciality]" value="<%= doctor.speciality %>" required>
                <div class="valid-feedback">
                    Looks Good!
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label" for="address">Work Address:</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" type="text" id="address" name="doctor[address]" required><%= doctor.address %></textarea>
                <div class="valid-feedback">
                    Looks Good!
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <button class="btn btn-success">Submit</button>
                <a href="/doctor/<%= doctor._id %>/info" class="btn btn-warning">Cancel</a>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="about">
            <img src="/photos/ChettinadLogo.PNG" alt="" style="border-radius: 10%; margin-left: 30px;">
            <br>
            <br>
            <h2>ABOUT</h2>
            <p>Chettinad Hospital & Research Institute (CHRI), a constituent college of Chettinad Academy of Research and Education (CARE), a Deemed to be University Under Section 3 of the UGC Act 1956 at Kelambakkam, Chennai through its primary health centre in the VIT, Vellore Campus provides round the clock primary (basic) health care services to all the students, staff and their dependents, faculty and their dependents and other employees working/residing at VIT Vellore Campus.</p>
            <br>
            <h2>FOLLOW US</h2>
            <h2>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-x-twitter"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i>
            </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="app">
            <h2>INSTALL APP</h2>
            <p>From App Store or Google Play</p>
            <h2>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-app-store"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-google-play"></i>
            </h2>
            <br><br><br>
            <h2>PAYMENT GATEWAYS</h2>
            <h2>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-cc-visa"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-cc-mastercard"></i> <br>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-cc-stripe"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-cc-paypal"></i>
            </h2>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>